-- Vale in Negotiations for Liberia Iron-Ore Mining Project, Reuters Reports
-- Laura Price
-- 2010-04-23T10:13:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/vale-in-negotiations-for-liberia-iron-ore-mining-project-reuters-reports.html

          
          
             Vale SA is in talks with Liberia’s 
government to explore for iron ore in the West African nation, 
Reuters reported, citing Richard Tolbert, chairman of the 
country’s National Investment Commission.  
 Vale and Liberia will “soon” make an announcement on the 
project, Reuters cited Tolbert as saying.   
